name: Rocket Forest
description: Rocket Forest is an oscilloscope-themed robot who is a proud member of the WebtrES Club. With its vibrant forest green box and classic button design, Rocket Forest stands out among its fellow robots. Equipped with rocket arms and legs, it has the ability to move swiftly and explore new territories. Its classic screen displays intricate waveforms and data, showcasing its exceptional intelligence and analytical skills. To enhance its safety, Rocket Forest is equipped with a protective helmet add-on, ensuring its resilience in any situation.
